			purpose = <"To assess if there is a need for further actions. ">
			use = <"To assessment is based on four parameters: decreased endurance, general fatigue/decreased strength in the last three months, often falls/thinks you will fall, need help making their purchases.

If the answer is Yes to 2 or more of these question it indicates need of further care. ">
